### 7. State Machine

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Checking: App mounts
    Checking --> Authenticated: Stored token is valid
    Checking --> Unauthenticated: No token or invalid
    Unauthenticated --> LoginView: Show login form
    LoginView --> Authenticating: User submits credentials
    Authenticating --> Authenticated: Login/register success
    Authenticating --> LoginView: Login fails (show error)
    Authenticated --> MainApp: Show nav-rail + views
    Authenticated --> Unauthenticated: 401 response or logout
    MainApp --> Unauthenticated: Token expires
```

### 8. Error Handling

| Error Scenario | Backend Response | Frontend Handling |
|----------------|------------------|-------------------|
| Missing Authorization header | 401 "Missing Authorization header" | `authFetch` clears token, shows LoginView |
| Expired JWT | 401 "Invalid token: ExpiredSignature" | Same as above |
| Invalid JWT signature | 401 "Invalid token: InvalidSignature" | Same as above |
| User deleted after token issued | 401 "User not found" | Same as above |
| Wrong username/password | 401 "Invalid credentials" | LoginView shows error message |
| Username taken on register | 409 "Username already exists" | LoginView shows error message |
| Password too short | 400 "Password must be at least 4 characters" | LoginView shows error message |
| Missing RBAC database | 500 on startup | Server won't start (fail-fast) |
| SQLite locked | 500 "INTERNAL_SERVER_ERROR" | Toast notification |

